story_opening = """\nYou wake up in a place you don’t recognize with a terrible headache. Looking at your surroundings, you seem to be in the entrance hall of a great and ominous mansion. Behind you is the door outside, but it’s locked, with spots for 3 keys necessary to open the door and escape. \n\nOn the ground before you is a walkie-talkie! After some experimentation, you learn that the device is tuned to three different people who can all speak through it: The Trickster, the Follower and the Seeker. You don’t know anything about them just yet beyond their names. Whoever they are, speaking with each of them and learning what they know might be the only way for you to find the 3 keys and escape. \n\nLooking around, the room has two stories with doors connecting this hall all throughout the mansion. There’s a door ahead of you that leads to the courtyard, doors to your sides that lead to the kitchen and further guest halls. The stairs ahead of you lead up into rooms unknown. \n\nWith the help of the voices through your walkie-talkie, you might be able to explore the mansion and find a way to escape. But who can you trust, how did you get here, and are you the only one here? Or are there dangers lurking just beyond this room? What do you do? (use @Trickster, @Follower or @Seeker to speak to others through the walkie-talkie)"""
